metadata.name: Positive Amplituhedron
metadata.description:
Scattered waveforms reveal a hidden reality in the space between us. Moving within the dissonance of constant reflection eventually dissolves all reality, leaving behind a metamagic essence. Harnessing this essence unlocks the doors of time. Fractured temporality becomes the vessel of interdimensional travel. Once the portal is crossed, chaos is unleashed.
